  namespace in `src/driver/Orchestrator.cpp`, called first in `initialize()`) refuses any
  `schema_version != "2.0"` and any missing required top-level section
  (`simulation/domain/time/modules/output`). `Config::validateSchema` is unchanged so
  component-level parsers (e.g. `SoluteParams::fromConfig`) can still exercise partial configs.
