  `migrateV1ToV2String`), CLI wrapper `tools/migrate_yaml_v1_to_v2.cpp` (`Frehg2::io`). Renames:
  `grid.*`→`domain.*` (+`bot_z`→`botz`), `time.{Tend,max_step,dt_out}`→`{t_end,max_steps,
  output_interval}` (+top-level `Tend`), `output.directory`/`io.dir`→`output.filename`,
  BC/source `type` short names→frozen vocabulary, `soil.uniform`+flat params→`soil.types[0]`.
  **Idempotent on v2** (renames only fire when the v1 key is present and the frozen key absent).
